spec_data.Name: perl-Math-Base85
spec_data.Description:
RFC 1924 describes a compact, fixed-size representation of IPv6 addresses
which uses a base 85 number system. This module handles some of the uglier
details of it.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Wed 18 Oct 2017 03:46:07 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Perl extension for base 85 numbers, as referenced by RFC 1924
